# Account Tools

Account tools is a django project for online password resets. It is currently on the Debian death.

It is installed as a python dist-package in _/usr/local/lib/python2.6/dist-packages/account\_tools_.

Note that the permissions of the account_tools package and the required LDAP and Kerberos files are finicky.

## Deploying Account Tools

1. Clone the git repo _supernova:/opt/src/users/kedo/account-tools_
2. Make sure the settings file exists at _/root/account\_tools\_settings.py.secret_
3. Run the setup script:

        $ python setup.py install
